## check the installed GNU Radio components 
	type in terminal
		gnuradio-config-info --enabled-components | sed 's/;/\n/g'
	source: https://wiki.gnuradio.org/index.php/FAQ#I_installed_GNU_Radio.2C_but_some_components_seem_to_be_missing.	

## adding osmocom for gr 3.8.3
	I used apt to install it 
		sudo apt-get update		
		sudo apt install gr-osmosdr
	
	[did not work properly] using git clone and cmake
		install git
			sudo apt install git-all
		if cmake is not installed
			sudo apt install cmake
		for latest version go to (using gr 3.9)
			https://osmocom.org/projects/gr-osmosdr/wiki/GrOsmoSDR
		or older version
			git clone https://github.com/osmocom/gr-osmosdr

